# Case 04 ‚Äì Advanced Insider Threat

## üìå Incident Summary
A suspicious internal user activity was detected involving unauthorized access to sensitive files, abnormal PowerShell execution, and potential data exfiltration attempts.

The activity originated from a legitimate employee account with valid credentials, indicating a possible advanced insider threat scenario.

---

## üïµÔ∏è Detection Source
- SIEM Alert (User Behavior Anomaly)
- PowerShell Logging
- File Access Audit Logs

